00:40:17,378 --> 00:40:21,382
<i>Born of the one light</i>

830
00:40:21,635 --> 00:40:25,050
<i>Eden saw play</i>

831
00:40:26,268 --> 00:40:30,683
<i>Praise with elation</i>

